Package: coresynth
Title: Fast and Unified Synthetic Control Methods
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yosuke Abe", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "yo5uke@duck.com")
Description: High-performance Synthetic Control Method (SCM) and related causal
    inference estimators (SDID, GSC, MC, TASC, SI) with a unified Formula
    interface. All computational bottlenecks (QP solving, SVD-based matrix
    completion, Kalman filtering) are implemented in C++ via RcppArmadillo,
    providing 10x-50x speed improvements over pure-R alternatives.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/yo5uke/coresynth
BugReports: https://github.com/yo5uke/coresynth/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
